OL,3,C'It's not a way to live': New study
OL,4,Coffers hope for Long Covid sufferers
OL,6,FA new study by researchers at the
OL,7,FUniversity of Exeter may offer a
OL,8,Fglimmer of hope to the estimated two
OL,9,Fmillion people in the UK struggling
OL,10,Fwith Long Covid.
OL,12,FThe Brain Training trial is hoped to
OL,13,Fhelp those suffering from brain fog -
OL,14,Fa common symptom of Long Covid.
OL,16,FAmber Rawlinson has been unable to
OL,17,Fwork since she got the disease in
OL,18,FNovember 2021.
OL,20,FShe rarely goes out, and everyday
OL,21,Fliving is exhausting.
