OL,3,C'It's not a way to live': New study
OL,4,Coffers hope for Long Covid sufferers
OL,6,FThe 22-year-old feels there is little
OL,7,Fsupport, treatment or even hope for
OL,8,Fher Long Covid symptoms.
OL,10,FShe said: "I very rarely have a good
OL,11,Fday but you never know when that day
OL,12,Fis going to come. You never know when
OL,13,Fyou're going to have a day when your
OL,14,Fsymptoms are calm and you're able to
OL,15,Fget out and do things.
OL,17,F"It's always quite a lot of planning
OL,18,Fahead, picking and choosing what to do
OL,19,Fand when.
OL,21,F"It's not really a way to live at all."
