OL,3,C'It's not a way to live': New study
OL,4,Coffers hope for Long Covid sufferers
OL,6,FVery little is known about why some
OL,7,Fpeople are affected by Long Covid.
OL,9,FThe Office for National Statistics
OL,10,F(ONS) has stopped collating figures
OL,11,Ffor the numbers involved - but at the
OL,12,Flast count, it was thought more than
OL,13,Ftwo million people in the UK have it.
OL,15,FAmber said: "It stops people from
OL,16,Fworking, it stops people from
OL,17,Fsocialising, it affects them mentally
OL,18,F- there's a lot to it.
OL,20,F"We're four years in now, and we still
OL,21,Fdon't really have any answers."
