OL,3,C'It's not a way to live': New study
OL,4,Coffers hope for Long Covid sufferers
OL,6,FNow the University of Exeter is at the
OL,7,Fforefront of research into the cause
OL,8,Fand treatments.
OL,10,FDr David Strain, the research lead for
OL,11,FLong Covid at the university, said:
OL,12,F"One thing that's really important is
OL,13,Fthat many people still have symptoms
OL,14,Fthree years after their infection.
OL,16,F"Realistically, if they get through
OL,17,Fthe first 12 months without showing
OL,18,Fmuch in the way of recovery, then it
OL,19,Fis very unlikely this disease is going
OL,20,Fto get better on its own.
