OL,3,C'It's not a way to live': New study
OL,4,Coffers hope for Long Covid sufferers
OL,6,F"That's why researching this condition
OL,7,Fis still a significant health service
OL,8,Fpriority."
OL,10,FTheir latest project, called Beacon,
OL,11,Fis based on work done with brain
OL,12,Ftraining puzzles on older adults who
OL,13,Fhad already shown signs of cognitive
OL,14,Fdecline.
OL,16,FThe hope is the puzzles will reduce
OL,17,Fthe impact of Long Covid on brain
OL,18,Ffunction.
