OL,3,C'It's not a way to live': New study
OL,4,Coffers hope for Long Covid sufferers
OL,6,FThe study will take six months, with
OL,7,Fpeople asked to do the puzzles for
OL,8,Faround 10 minutes a day. If
OL,9,Fsuccessful, it could be a cost-
OL,10,Feffective treatment for one of the
OL,11,Fmost common symptoms of Long Covid.
OL,13,FProfessor Anne Corbett, from the
OL,14,Funiversity, said: "We know it's not a
OL,15,Fsilver bullet. It's not going to be
OL,16,Fthe only treatment but it can be just
OL,17,Fmade freely available to anyone that
OL,18,Fwants it and I think that is really
OL,19,Fimportant.
