OL,3,C'It's not a way to live': New study
OL,4,Coffers hope for Long Covid sufferers
OL,6,F"We know there are two million people
OL,7,Fin the UK with Long Covid, we know
OL,8,Fthat at least 50 per cent of those
OL,9,Fhave experienced some kind of brain
OL,10,Ffog, that's a large number of people.
OL,11,FWe've got to make this cost effective."
OL,13,FFor people like Amber, who has felt
OL,14,Fout on a limb with her long covid
OL,15,Fjourney, any research is good news.
OL,16,FShe just hopes it will lead to more
OL,17,Funderstanding and a cure for this
OL,18,Flittle known but terribly debilitating
OL,19,Fcondition.
